				<div class="comment-body"><p>What is the difference between a &#8216;novella&#8217; and a &#8216;novelette&#8217;? May I submit a work of short stories that includes a fantasy short story, separately. Would I then have to ensure that the book is published by one of your approved publishers? The other stories are neither sci-fi nor fantasy.</p>
</div>

				<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='index.html?replytocom=469132#respond' data-commentid="469132" data-postid="2449" data-belowelement="comment-469132" data-respondelement="respond" aria-label='Reply to John P. McWilliams'>Reply</a>				</div><!-- .reply -->
