				<div class="comment-body"><p>According to MidAmeriCon II, the <a href="../../../2016/04/2016-hugo-awards-shortlist-to-be-announced-april-26/index.html" rel="nofollow">Hugo Award finalists will be announced on April 26, 2016</a>.</p>
<p>We no longer use the term &#8220;nominations&#8221; to describe the shortlist of finalists due to persistent deceptive misuse of the term by other people. WSFS officially abandoned its use in 2015. People who appear on the final ballot are &#8220;finalists&#8221; and appear on the &#8220;shortlist.&#8221;</p>
</div>

